---
import Card from "../Card/index.astro";
---

<Card
  colSpan="md:col-span-1"
  rowSpan="md:row-span-6"
  title="Other things about me"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      I developed this tiny resume and published it using AWS.
      I'm in a poly relationship with Docker and Laravel.
      <br />
      <br />
      Jokes aside, I know both deeply because I use them daily. I've
      also developed a package which helps me when starting a new Laravel project
      and automate the recurring (and boring) actions.
    </p>
    <ul class="text-sm font-light">
      I've been able to integrate a lot of technologies in the projects I've made, such
      as:
      <li class="text-sm font-light">· Elasticsearch</li>
      <li class="text-sm font-light">· Google</li>
      <li class="text-sm font-light">· ChatGPT</li>
      <li class="text-sm font-light">· and more...</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-sm font-light">
      With them, I developed a documents search engine.
      <br />
      (©weconstudio)
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>
